The native compiler used to accept the following code, and Roslyn follows suit:

``` c#
class Program
{
    static void M() { }
    public static void Main(string[] args)
    {
        var a = new System.Action(ref M);
    }
}
```

We correctly diagnose the error in "strict" mode.  See also #2249.

Please diagnose this issue in a warning wave.
